data.oai_dc:dc: Measurements of water column depth at 15 minute intervals in the Parker River near Rt 1A bridge, year 2000. Water depths are relative to the sonde pressure transducer and not associated with a datum.
15 minute readings of water column depth in the lower Parker River Estuary at Rt. 1A. Water depths are relative to the sonde pressure transducer and not associated with a datum.
